{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "chitchat-v5.1-2026",
    "name": "ChitChat V5.1 AI - Complete API Collection",
    "description": "üöÄ **COMPLETE POSTMAN COLLECTION** - ChitChat V5.1 AI\n\n**Last Updated:** January 2026\n\n**üìã FEATURES:**\n- üîê Authentication (Register, NextAuth)\n- üë• Friends Management\n- üè† Rooms (Private, Group, AI)\n- üí¨ Messages with Attachments\n- ü§ñ AI Chat Integration\n- üë§ Profile Management\n- üîí Password Management\n- üì§ File Uploads\n\n**üîß HOW TO USE:**\n1. Import this collection to Postman\n2. Run **Register** to create new user\n3. Set environment variables:\n   - `user_id`: your userId from register\n   - `api_key`: secretbet\n4. All other requests use auto-headers\n\n**üîê AUTHENTICATION:**\nHeaders (auto-added for all requests except Register):\n- `x-api-key: {{api_key}}`\n- `x-user-id: {{user_id}}`\n\n**üìç BASE URL:** http://localhost:1630",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:1630",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "api_key",
      "value": "secretbet",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "user_id",
      "value": "user001",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "last_room_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "friend_user_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "if (!pm.request.url.path.includes('register')) {",
          "    pm.request.headers.upsert({",
          "        key: 'x-api-key',",
          "        value: pm.collectionVariables.get('api_key') || 'secretbet',",
          "        type: 'text'",
          "    });",
          "    pm.request.headers.upsert({",
          "        key: 'x-user-id',",
          "        value: pm.collectionVariables.get('user_id') || 'user001',",
          "        type: 'text'",
          "    });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
